{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day after three weeks, weeks without anything at all, marching to work, we're taken away, again in a train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, without our menashkas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we ended up in a place called Helmstedt, a very small place where they have never seen Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mostly they were prisoners of war, German criminals, and a mixture of things, about, perhaps, four, five, six, seven all together, including us, 150 of us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had no work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I soon found work-- artificial work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It must have been on a hill because we went downward, downhill for 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was light and easy and wonderful in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But in the evening, to go uphill after being beaten terribly, hard work, and little food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, our group shrunk and shrunk very quickly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And again, we did something which only we could do because we had two of us sticking together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I found there was a nearby hut.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And inside the hut were a lot of boxes on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I climbed on top of the boxes and down the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one of the-- I put one of the boxes on top of me and there I could rest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, probably, well of course, we exchanged with our-- we changed over from time to time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If my father would either whistle or throw a stone, it would be the sign either to go home or to change or danger or anything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, this helped us a great deal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I could swear that the other one was helped by knowing the hard worker was helped knowing the other one had to rest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
